6
00:01:53,190 --> 00:01:54,050
Grandma.

7
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:56,100
I'm finally in Italy.

8
00:01:57,090 --> 00:01:58,240
Do you remember

9
00:01:58,630 --> 00:02:00,790
