27
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:03,190
It's less than 100 years old.

28
00:03:03,190 --> 00:03:05,100
I suggest we…

29
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:06,270
Are you sure?

30
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:10,120
Are there no other possibilities?

31
00:03:10,610 --> 00:03:11,490
Mayor,

32
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,180
Curator Chen is right.

33
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:14,360
Actually,

34
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,010
