35
00:03:16,010 --> 00:03:17,750
to stop the excavation.

36
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:20,180
It's going to keep raining.

37
00:03:20,210 --> 00:03:22,579
The drainage and protection work

38
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,700
will consume a lot of manpower and resources.

39
00:03:24,700 --> 00:03:26,490
Our budget is limited.

40
00:03:27,250 --> 00:03:28,310
Let's stop

41
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,579
excavating this ship, shall we?

42
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:31,870
We should spend the money on

43
00:03:31,870 --> 00:03:33,400
more meaningful projects.

44
00:03:37,290 --> 00:03:38,020
Alright.

45
00:03:39,850 --> 00:03:41,370
I respect your opinions.

46
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,410
Let's stop then.

47
00:03:46,570 --> 00:03:47,610
Guys.

48
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,590
Today is our last day

49
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:50,590
at the 116th shipwreck

50
00:03:50,590 --> 00:03:51,850
archaeological site.

51
00:03:51,930 --> 00:03:52,310
Mom!

52
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:53,220
We shall…

53
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:53,710
Mom!

54
00:03:53,710 --> 00:03:55,360
complete all

55
00:03:55,850 --> 00:03:57,510
-the related paperwork
-Mom!

56
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,630
by 5 p.m.

57
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:00,190
The excavation finally restarted.

58
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:02,050
Why are you suddenly stopping it?

59
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:03,180
Who are you

60
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:05,750
to ask me that?

61
00:04:06,450 --> 00:04:07,630
My son?

62
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,400
Or…

63
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,530
I'm a volunteer at the shipwreck site.

64
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:15,860
The decision has been made

65
00:04:15,890 --> 00:04:17,300
and announced.

66
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,730
The shipwreck excavation is stopped.

67
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,260
Don't waste any more time here.

68
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:25,170
I'm wasting my time?

69
00:04:25,890 --> 00:04:27,770
Then what isn't a waste of time?

70
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:30,900
Should I sit in an office drinking hot tea

71
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,320
and doing field research

72
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,510
or stay in a library traveling around

73
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:35,360
through a few hardcover books?

74
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:37,170
That's not a waste of time?

75
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:39,610
Yeah, I know you're not satisfied with me.

76
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:41,680
I didn't listen to you about which college to attend

77
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:43,270
or about what job to take.

78
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:44,600
But do you think I'm here today

79
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,360
just to stand against you?

80
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:50,230
So you know what you've done.

81
00:04:51,090 --> 00:04:51,690
Yes.

82
00:04:54,340 --> 00:04:55,700
You're my son.

83
00:04:56,570 --> 00:04:58,730
I am very disappointed in you.

84
00:05:01,030 --> 00:05:02,440
But today,

85
00:05:03,330 --> 00:05:04,810
we'll only talk about work.

86
00:05:04,810 --> 00:05:05,930
Nothing personal.

87
00:05:06,860 --> 00:05:08,790
I didn't make this decision.

88
00:05:09,420 --> 00:05:11,140
The experts have confirmed

89
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,230
that this ship

90
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:13,920
has no excavation value.

91
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:14,960
Mayor Gu.

92
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:16,190
Mayor Gu.

93
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:18,680
What does this ship mean to you?

94
00:05:18,710 --> 00:05:21,340
Is it just a cultural site for show

95
00:05:21,540 --> 00:05:24,620
and a mere tool for Honghuai City's application for World Heritage status?

96
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:26,040
Now that the canal has become a World Heritage Site,

97
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,190
it's of no use to you anymore,

98
00:05:27,190 --> 00:05:28,160
so you're just throwing it away?

99
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,360
You're going too far!

100
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,370
That's total nonsense!

101
00:05:32,659 --> 00:05:33,800
Do you know

102
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:35,000
what happened on this ship

103
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,560
and who lived on it?

104
00:05:36,580 --> 00:05:37,630
You don't!

105
00:05:37,630 --> 00:05:38,930
They don't!

106
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:41,640
How can you say it's worthless?

107
00:05:42,590 --> 00:05:45,340
There were real people living on this ship.

108
00:05:45,690 --> 00:05:47,920
They might have been insignificant.

109
00:05:47,970 --> 00:05:49,060
They might have been

110
00:05:49,060 --> 00:05:50,380
of no value at all

111
00:05:50,409 --> 00:05:51,730
in the long history.

112
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:53,990
But to their descendants and loved ones,

113
00:05:53,990 --> 00:05:56,150
they were of immense value.

114
00:05:56,580 --> 00:05:58,860
And we've been looking for traces.

115
00:05:58,890 --> 00:06:00,710
They could very well be the ancestors

116
00:06:00,710 --> 00:06:01,370
of the uncles and aunts,

117
00:06:01,370 --> 00:06:03,030
grandpas and grandmas in the courtyard.

118
00:06:03,030 --> 00:06:04,950
If I can prove that,

119
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:05,830
I can prove…

120
00:06:05,850 --> 00:06:08,380
But the government's budget is limited!

121
00:06:08,530 --> 00:06:10,180
Now that the canal has become a World Heritage Site,

122
00:06:10,180 --> 00:06:13,160
the entire Honghuai is facing renovation and reconstruction.

123
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,300
Let me ask you.

124
00:06:14,470 --> 00:06:15,510
Should the government

125
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:16,540
spend the money

126
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,800
on reconstruction that's closely related

127
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,560
to people's lives

128
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,720
or on a sunken ship

129
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,560
that experts have said

130
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,070
to be worthless?

131
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,030
Okay.

132
00:06:31,390 --> 00:06:32,100
I got it.

133
00:06:34,570 --> 00:06:35,770
Then please allow me,

134
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,830
on behalf of Grandpa Zhou,

135
00:06:38,830 --> 00:06:40,740
my family in the courtyard,

136
00:06:43,330 --> 00:06:45,540
and Ma Siyi to whom I made a promise,

137
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:48,170
to formally request

138
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:51,230
that you transfer the excavation of the sunken ship

139
00:06:51,230 --> 00:06:52,250
to me.

140
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:55,580
I'll raise funds myself to complete the subsequent work.

141
00:06:56,550 --> 00:06:57,980
I'll prove to you

142
00:06:58,909 --> 00:07:01,080
that the place you think is meaningless

143
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:02,810
