145
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,580
there will be new choices;

146
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,030
the boy

147
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:12,250
who is worthless in the eyes of the world

148
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:16,340
